      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "真实交付：\n- frozen_portfolio_spec.json 或 portfolio_contract.yaml\n- portfolio_weight_panel.parquet\n- portfolio_curve.parquet 或 portfolio_summary.parquet\n- engine_compare.csv\n- vectorbt/ 与 backtrader/\n- strategy_combo_ledger.csv 或 rebalance_ledger.csv\n- capacity_review.md / turnover_capacity / cost_assumption\n- artifact_catalog.md / field_dictionary.md\n\n实现提醒：\n- author / review 对交付物命名和颗粒度不完全一致，research repo 里要统一正式文件名并在 artifact_catalog 写映射\n- 这里冻结的是组合合同，不是再解释 factor 意义\n- Holdout 将只复用这里冻结好的组合方案\n- 通过 review closure 后，才进入 08 CSF Holdout Validation",
      "rawText": "真实交付：\n- frozen_portfolio_spec.json 或 portfolio_contract.yaml\n- portfolio_weight_panel.parquet\n- portfolio_curve.parquet 或 portfolio_summary.parquet\n- engine_compare.csv\n- vectorbt/ 与 backtrader/\n- strategy_combo_ledger.csv 或 rebalance_ledger.csv\n- capacity_review.md / turnover_capacity / cost_assumption\n- artifact_catalog.md / field_dictionary.md\n\n实现提醒：\n- author / review 对交付物命名和颗粒度不完全一致，research repo 里要统一正式文件名并在 artifact_catalog 写映射\n- 这里冻结的是组合合同，不是再解释 factor 意义\n- Holdout 将只复用这里冻结好的组合方案\n- 通过 review closure 后，才进入 08 CSF Holdout Validation",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "真实交付：\n- frozen_portfolio_spec.json 或 portfolio_contract.yaml\n- portfolio_weight_panel.parquet\n- portfolio_curve.parquet 或 portfolio_summary.parquet\n- engine_compare.csv\n- vectorbt/ 与 backtrader/\n- strategy_combo_ledger.csv 或 rebalance_ledger.csv\n- capacity_review.md / turnover_capacity / cost_assumption\n- artifact_catalog.md / field_dictionary.md\n\n实现提醒：\n- author / review 对交付物命名和颗粒度不完全一致，research repo 里要统一正式文件名并在 artifact_catalog 写映射\n- 这里冻结的是组合合同，不是再解释 factor 意义\n- Holdout 将只复用这里冻结好的组合方案\n- 通过 review closure 后，才进入 08 CSF Holdout Validation",
